epKoamaru" id="learn-more-changemaker" href="/programs/changemaker/" class="link__StyledLink-sc-sk2fkb-0 elsGvp link__StyledLink-sc-sk2fkb-0 elsGvp"><div class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 lnSPAF">Learn More about the Changemaker Program</div></a></div></div></div></div></section><section width="1" color="greys.1" id="rebel-support" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 htvAlv"><div width="1" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 fFkUTz"><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 kOkOem"><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 bOThJ"><h2 class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 heading__Heading-sc-8y1gmp-0 dPjPJB llvEqk"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="title" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 ituCVP"><div class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 dJwlBi content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">The Rebel difference: Award Winning<br> Customer Support</div></div></div></h2></div><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="body" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 kGLXQD"><div class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 gDIDup content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">Ever notice how problems tend to pop up when there's no one around to help you? Well, with Rebel, you're never on your own. If you have any questions regarding your website, you can always talk to someone. <br><br>Our in-house team of knowledgeable agents (located in Ottawa, Canada) <br>are happy to help you out via email 24/7, and through live chat 8am-10pm,<br> or phone support 9am-5pm ET, seven days a week.</div></div></div></div><div display="grid" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 jNIQpQ"><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 cFWBDK"><div class="image__Img-es1yyv-0 bSzEnP gatsby-image-wrapper" style="position:relative;overflow:hidden"><div aria-hidden="true" style="width:100%;padding-bottom:66.66666666666667%"></div><img aria-hidden="true" src="data:image/png;base64," alt=