/cms-assets/static/707dcd061aee919e79c108e0ce23c09b/6e312/helpfulman.jpg 1733w" src="/cms-assets/static/707dcd061aee919e79c108e0ce23c09b/88d35/helpfulman.jpg" alt="Man holding papers and smiling at laptop" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center"/></picture></noscript></div></div></div></div></div></section><section width="1" id="faq" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 ebZVzS"><div width="1" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 ixGzjh"><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 fNwgmI"><h2 class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 heading__Heading-sc-8y1gmp-0 dPjPJB llvEqk"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="title" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 ituCVP"><div class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 bDdNsX content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">Frequently asked questions</div></div></div></h2></div><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 fXgVww"><div width="100%" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 kaUcoV"><button display="flex" type="button" class="button__StyledButton-sc-1h5r8gm-0 ecUnnD accordion___StyledButton-sc-1tvxo61-2 hXUUGK"><div display="grid" width="1" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 dPREw"><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 fNwgmI"><h2 class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 heading__Heading-sc-8y1gmp-0 kcFlGN llvEqk"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="title" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 SfctJ"><div class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 bCWTZC content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">How does Rebel help small business owners succeed?</div></div></div></h2></div></div><div class="accordion__IconBox-sc-1tvxo61-1 iGvoPJ"><div height="3rem" width="4rem" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 bRWJnq"><svg height="3rem" role="img" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" width="4rem" class="icon__SVG-sc-fuh9x1-0 bWSOBh"><title>back</title><path d="M487.456 613.6l24.128 24.16 193.12-193.152-24.128-24.128-168.992 168.992-168.192-168.192-24.128 24.128 168.192 168.192z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div></button><div overflow="hidden" width="100%" class="accordion__ContentPane-sc-1tvxo61-0 bjbQZt"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="body" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 lkvgme"><div font-size="1" class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 cLqfuh content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">Entrepreneurs have enough on their plates without having to stress about getting and managing their professional image online. Whether you're starting your first business website or simply looking to work with a more reliable partner, Rebel makes it easy to set up or migrate what you already have, for free. Our support team is standing by to help you with everything from buying domains, choosing the right web hosting service, to setting up your professional email. If you're looking to optimize your site's security and Google rankings, Rebel gives you the keys to unlock success.</div></div></div></div></div><div width="100%" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 kaUcoV"><button display="flex" type="button" class="button__StyledButton-sc-1h5r8gm-0 ecUnnD accordion___StyledButton-sc-1tvxo61-2 hXUUGK"><div display="grid" width="1" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 dPREw"><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 fNwgmI"><h2 class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 heading__Heading-sc-8y1gmp-0 kcFlGN llvEqk"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="title" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 SfctJ"><div class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 bCWTZC content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">Why do I need a website for my business?</div></div></div></h2></div></div><div class="accordion__IconBox-sc-1tvxo61-1 iGvoPJ"><div height="3rem" width="4rem" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 bRWJnq"><svg height="3rem" role="img" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" width="4rem" class="icon__SVG-sc-fuh9x1-0 bWSOBh"><title>back</title><path d="M487.456 613.6l24.128 24.16 193.12-193.152-24.128-24.128-168.992 168.992-168.192-168.192-24.128 24.128 168.192 168.192z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div></button><div overflow="hidden" width="100%" class="accordion__ContentPane-sc-1tvxo61-0 bjbQZt"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="body" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 lkvgme"><div font-size="1" class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 cLqfuh content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">A strong digital presence is a must-have for today's businesses. That's because customers expect to find you online. Whether it's a website, an e-commerce platform, a social media page or a combination of all three, getting your company online comes with major benefits. <ul><li>Visibility: Make it easy for customers and prospects to find you.</li> <li>Credibility: A professional website is the face of your brand. It builds trust.</li><li>Reach: A site lets you market your brand effectively, tying it to social media.</li><li>Creating a comprehensive digital presence is key to having a thriving business. And with Rebel, the journey to get there is smooth, secure, seamless and fully supported. It's also easier and more affordable than you might think.</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div width="100%" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 kaUcoV"><button display="flex" type="button" class="button__StyledButton-sc-1h5r8gm-0 ecUnnD accordion___StyledButton-sc-1tvxo61-2 hXUUGK"><div display="grid" width="1" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 dPREw"><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 fNwgmI"><h2 class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 heading__Heading-sc-8y1gmp-0 kcFlGN llvEqk"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="title" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 SfctJ"><div class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 bCWTZC content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">Why use Rebel to build your website?</div></div></div></h2></div></div><div class="accordion__IconBox-sc-1tvxo61-1 iGvoPJ"><div height="3rem" width="4rem" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 bRWJnq"><svg height="3rem" role="img" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" width="4rem" class="icon__SVG-sc-fuh9x1-0 bWSOBh"><title>back</title><path d="M487.456 613.6l24.128 24.16 193.12-193.152-24.128-24.128-168.992 168.992-168.192-168.192-24.128 24.128 168.192 168.192z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div></button><div overflow="hidden" width="100%" class="accordion__ContentPane-sc-1tvxo61-0 bjbQZt"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="body" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 lkvgme"><div font-size="1" class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 cLqfuh content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">You get all the tools you need to create a site that's unique to you without any technical expertise. This includes: <ul><li>Modern, professional and beautiful templates</li><li>Drag & drop builder tools</li><li>Powerful e-commerce tools</li><li>Optional website design packages</li><li>Free SSL certificate, SEO and analytics included in our plans</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div width="100%" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 kaUcoV"><button display="flex" type="button" class="button__StyledButton-sc-1h5r8gm-0 ecUnnD accordion___StyledButton-sc-1tvxo61-2 hXUUGK"><div display="grid" width="1" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 dPREw"><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 fNwgmI"><h2 class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 heading__Heading-sc-8y1gmp-0 kcFlGN llvEqk"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="title" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 SfctJ"><div class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 bCWTZC content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">Why get a domain name from Rebel?</div></div></div></h2></div></div><div class="accordion__IconBox-sc-1tvxo61-1 iGvoPJ"><div height="3rem" width="4rem" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 bRWJnq"><svg height="3rem" role="img" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" width="4rem" class="icon__SVG-sc-fuh9x1-0 bWSOBh"><title>back</title><path d="M487.456 613.6l24.128 24.16 193.12-193.152-24.128-24.128-168.992 168.992-168.192-168.192-24.128 24.128 168.192 168.192z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div></button><div overflow="hidden" width="100%" class="accordion__ContentPane-sc-1tvxo61-0 bjbQZt"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="body" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 lkvgme"><div font-size="1" class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 cLqfuh content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">If you own a business, Rebel can help you find the perfect domain to represent you. But Rebel isn't just about domain names. We've got everything you need to get online. From web hosting to custom design for your website and tools for attracting new traffic, Rebel's got you covered. And who doesn't love managing everything in one place?</div></div></div></div></div><div width="100%" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 kaUcoV"><button display="flex" type="button" class="button__StyledButton-sc-1h5r8gm-0 ecUnnD accordion___StyledButton-sc-1tvxo61-2 hXUUGK"><div display="grid" width="1" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 dPREw"><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 fNwgmI"><h2 class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 heading__Heading-sc-8y1gmp-0 kcFlGN llvEqk"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="title" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 SfctJ"><div class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 bCWTZC content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">Why do I need a professional email?</div></div></div></h2></div></div><div class="accordion__IconBox-sc-1tvxo61-1 iGvoPJ"><div height="3rem" width="4rem" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 bRWJnq"><svg height="3rem" role="img" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" width="4rem" class="icon__SVG-sc-fuh9x1-0 bWSOBh"><title>back</title><path d="M487.456 613.6l24.128 24.16 193.12-193.152-24.128-24.128-168.992 168.992-168.192-168.192-24.128 24.128 168.192 168.192z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div></button><div overflow="hidden" width="100%" class="accordion__ContentPane-sc-1tvxo61-0 bjbQZt"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="body" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 lkvgme"><div font-size="1" class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 cLqfuh content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">Frankly, not having a custom personal email address in the digital age is risky. There are many reasons to match your domain to your email address and these are our top three: <ul><li>Adds authenticity: Your email address sends a message to customers before you do.</li><li>Strengthens security: A custom email address gets top-notch spam and virus filters.</li><li>Boosts your brand: Regardless of whether you have a storefront or not, a custom email address puts your business name where it can easily be found.</li></ul><br>Remember, domains are used for email addresses and websites. You can have a custom email address even if you decide to do nothing else with your domain. With Rebel, you always get free assisted email migration and setup.</div></div></div></div></div><div width="100%" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 kaUcoV"><button display="flex" type="button" class="button__StyledButton-sc-1h5r8gm-0 ecUnnD accordion___StyledButton-sc-1tvxo61-2 hXUUGK"><div display="grid" width="1" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 dPREw"><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 fNwgmI"><h2 class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 heading__Heading-sc-8y1gmp-0 kcFlGN llvEqk"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="title" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 SfctJ"><div class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 bCWTZC content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">What makes Rebel Web Hosting trusted by customers in 186 countries?</div></div></div></h2></div></div><div class="accordion__IconBox-sc-1tvxo61-1 iGvoPJ"><div height="3rem" width="4rem" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 bRWJnq"><svg height="3rem" role="img" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" width="4rem" class="icon__SVG-sc-fuh9x1-0 bWSOBh"><title>back</title><path d="M487.456 613.6l24.128 24.16 193.12-193.152-24.128-24.128-168.992 168.992-168.192-168.192-24.128 24.128 168.192 168.192z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div></button><div overflow="hidden" width="100%" class="accordion__ContentPane-sc-1tvxo61-0 bjbQZt"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="body" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 lkvgme"><div font-size="1" class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 cLqfuh content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0"><ul><li>Fast page load times. Really fast. Like 200 milliseconds or less.</li><li>Free Site Migration: Rebel will help you move an existing website — and email — to our secure servers at no charge. Expect virtually no interruption in service.</li><li>Award Winning Customer Support: You can talk to a real person at any time.</li><li>99.99% uptime guarantee: Yes, your site will be available at least 99.99% of the time.</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div width="100%" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 kaUcoV"><button display="flex" type="button" class="button__StyledButton-sc-1h5r8gm-0 ecUnnD accordion___StyledButton-sc-1tvxo61-2 hXUUGK"><div display="grid" width="1" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 dPREw"><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 fNwgmI"><h2 class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 heading__Heading-sc-8y1gmp-0 kcFlGN llvEqk"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="title" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 SfctJ"><div class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 bCWTZC content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">Why choose Rebel for WordPress?</div></div></div></h2></div></div><div class="accordion__IconBox-sc-1tvxo61-1 iGvoPJ"><div height="3rem" width="4rem" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 bRWJnq"><svg height="3rem" role="img" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" width="4rem" class="icon__SVG-sc-fuh9x1-0 bWSOBh"><title>back</title><path d="M487.456 613.6l24.128 24.16 193.12-193.152-24.128-24.128-168.992 168.992-168.192-168.192-24.128 24.128 168.192 168.192z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div></button><div overflow="hidden" width="100%" class="accordion__ContentPane-sc-1tvxo61-0 bjbQZt"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="body" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 lkvgme"><div font-size="1" class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 cLqfuh content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">Love your WordPress site but hate the maintenance? With Managed WordPress we look after the updates, backups, patches, and malware removal so you've got more time to build your business and your online community. Add to that, access to our award-winning support, free hosting migration, and a 30-day money back guarantee. If you already have a website, but are not happy with its performance, Rebel also offers a tune-up package to get your WordPress site humming along in no time.</div></div></div></div></div><div width="100%" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 kaUcoV"><button display="flex" type="button" class="button__StyledButton-sc-1h5r8gm-0 ecUnnD accordion___StyledButton-sc-1tvxo61-2 hXUUGK"><div display="grid" width="1" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 dPREw"><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 fNwgmI"><h2 class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 heading__Heading-sc-8y1gmp-0 kcFlGN llvEqk"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="title" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 SfctJ"><div class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 bCWTZC content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">Why should I transfer my domain, website or web hosting to Rebel?</div></div></div></h2></div></div><div class="accordion__IconBox-sc-1tvxo61-1 iGvoPJ"><div height="3rem" width="4rem" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 bRWJnq"><svg height="3rem" role="img" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" width="4rem" class="icon__SVG-sc-fuh9x1-0 bWSOBh"><title>back</title><path d="M487.456 613.6l24.128 24.16 193.12-193.152-24.128-24.128-168.992 168.992-168.192-168.192-24.128 24.128 168.192 168.192z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div></button><div overflow="hidden" width="100%" class="accordion__ContentPane-sc-1tvxo61-0 bjbQZt"><div display="flex" class="style-reset__StyleReset-sc-19u980z-0 gFcQco"><div color="greys.1" font-family="body" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 lkvgme"><div font-size="1" class="html-block__Block-sc-1dm9fyv-0 cLqfuh content___StyledHtmlBlock-sc-1lhrlny-0">Your website is your #1 marketing asset and it needs to work for you―and your customers. When you partner with Rebel, you get a 99.9% uptime guarantee. Simply put, that means when customers visit your website, it'll be available and it will load super fast. This accessibility is critical to your online success. If your site is slow to load, customers will go elsewhere and you might not even realize that's happening. Rebel ensures your site loads in 200ms or less which is why our migration experts are so busy transferring customers' websites (and email), domains and web hosting over to our powerful servers. That, and the fact that they make the switch so easy and seamless.</div></div></div></div></div><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How does Rebel help small business owners succeed?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Entrepreneurs have enough on their plates without having to stress about getting and managi