 find the perfect domain to represent you. But Rebel isn't just about domain names. We've got everything you need to get online. From web hosting to custom design for your website and tools for attracting new traffic, Rebel's got you covered. And who doesn't love managing everything in one place?"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Why do I need a professional email?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Frankly, not having a custom personal email address in the digital age is risky. There are many reasons to match your domain to your email address and these are our top three: <ul><li>Adds authenticity: Your email address sends a message to customers before you do.</li><li>Strengthens security: A custom email address gets top-notch spam and virus filters.</li><li>Boosts your brand: Regardless of whether you have a storefront or not, a custom email address puts your business name where it can easily be found.</li></ul><br>Remember, domains are used for email addresses and websites. You can have a custom email address even if you decide to do nothing else with your domain. With Rebel, you always get free assisted email migration and setup."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What makes Rebel Web Hosting trusted by customers in 186 countries?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<ul><li>Fast page load times. Really fast. Like 200 milliseconds or less.</li><li>Free Site Migration: Rebel will help you move an existing website — and email — to our secure servers at no charge. Expect virtually no interruption in service.</li><li>Award Winning Customer Support: You can talk to a real person at any time.</li><li>99.99% uptime guarantee: Yes, your site will be available at least 99.99% of the time.</li></ul>"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Why choose Rebel for WordPress?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Love your WordPress site but hate the maintenance? With Managed WordPress we look after the updates, backups, patches, and malware removal so you've got more time to build your business and your online community. Add to that, access to our award-winning support, free hosting migration, and a 30-day money back guarantee. If you already have a website, but are not happy with its performance, Rebel also offers a tune-up package to get your WordPress site humming along in no time."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Why should I transfer my domain, website or web hosting to Rebel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Your website is your #1 marketing asset and it needs to work for you―and your customers. When you partner with Rebel, you get a 99.9% uptime guarantee. Simply put, that means when customers visit your website, it'll be available and it will load super fast. This accessibility is critical to your online success. If your site is slow to load, customers will go elsewhere and you might not even realize that's happening. Rebel ensures your site loads in 200ms or less which is why our migration experts are so busy transferring customers' websites (and email), domains and web hosting over to our powerful servers. That, and the fact that they make the switch so easy and seamless."}}]}</script></div></div></section></main><footer><div color="white" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 iMWLej"><h2 color="white" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 heading__Heading-sc-8y1gmp-0 vUGKP llvEqk">Award-winning support</h2><div color="white" class="text__Text-sc-78yxcw-0 gVKsOG">Speak to real humans</div><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 czbunW"><div display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 eBPjlm"><div height="35" width="35" display="flex" class="box__Box-sc-1195mmx-0 kZGtyv"><svg aria-labelledby="start-chatting" height="35" role="img" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" width="35" class="icon__SVG-sc-fuh9x1-0 bWSOBh"><title id="start-chatting">Chat with us</title><path d="M170.667 434.603h221.867c9.438 0 17.067-7.646 17.067-17.067s-7.629-17.067-17.067-17.067h-221.867c-9.438 0-17.067 7.646-17.067 17.067s7.629 17.067 17.067 1